    {
      "num": 4,
      "title": "メカニズム：なぜ血糖正常のままDKAに？",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "SGLT2阻害薬による尿糖排泄で血糖低下→インスリン分泌低下→脂肪分解亢進→ケトン産生増加。同時にグルカゴン分泌増加とケトン体腎再吸収増加が重なり、血糖は上がらないのにケトアシドーシスが進行する。",
      "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 48px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);padding:4px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700}.main{display:flex;align-items:center;height:540px;padding:0 48px}.left-panel{flex:1}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 48px;font-size:13px;opacity:.5}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:28px}.flow-container{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:24px}.flow-box{background:rgba(20,184,166,.15);border:1px solid rgba(20,184,166,.4);padding:12px 20px;border-radius:12px;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;text-align:center}.flow-arrow{font-size:28px;color:#14b8a6}.sub-point{font-size:22px;line-height:1.7;opacity:.85;margin-top:8px;padding-left:8px}.accent{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:900}.point-box{border-left:5px solid #e74c3c;background:rgba(231,76,60,.1);padding:18px 24px;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;margin-top:24px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;font-weight:700}</style><div class='slide slide-dark'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>4 / 9</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='main'><div class='left-panel'><h2>なぜ血糖正常のままDKAになるのか？</h2><div class='flow-container'><span class='flow-box'>尿糖排泄↑</span><span class='flow-arrow'>→</span><span class='flow-box'>血糖低下</span><span class='flow-arrow'>→</span><span class='flow-box'>インスリン分泌↓</span><span class='flow-arrow'>→</span><span class='flow-box'>脂肪分解↑</span><span class='flow-arrow'>→</span><span class='flow-box'>ケトン産生↑</span></div><p class='sub-point'>＋ <span class='accent'>グルカゴン分泌↑</span>（さらに脂肪分解を促進）</p><p class='sub-point'>＋ <span class='accent'>ケトン体の腎再吸収↑</span>（排泄されにくい）</p><div class='point-box'>血糖は上がらないのに<br>ケトアシドーシスだけが進行する</div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
